abstract: Buffalo Bills wide receiver Marquise Goodwin takes second place in long jump at Pan American Games in Toronto.
lead_paragraph: Buffalo Bills wide receiver Marquise Goodwin won a silver medal in the long jump at the Pan American Games in Toronto.

headline.main: Bills’ Marquise Goodwin Is Second in Long Jump
